        <page0>Bonzi and the Treasure Chest!</page0>
        <page1>It was early in the morning when Bonzi and Spot set out along the beach to collect seashells! Today was Effie's Birthday and they wanted to make her a present! The fog was so thick it made it hard for them to see! But that didn't stop them! Tonight was her surprise party and they still had a lot to do! \Pit=50\"Ouch!" \Pit=140\screamed Bonzi. \Pit=400\\Spd=175\"What is it? Are you okay?" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\replied Spot. \Pit=50\"My toe! I stubbed my toe on this big rock!" \Pit=140\cried Bonzi. \Pit=400\\Spd=175\"That's not a rock, Bonzi. It's some sort of box," \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Spot. Upon a closer look, Bonzi yelled, \Pit=50\"That's not a box, Spot, it's a Treasure Chest!" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\Together they jumped up and down, laughing and clapping until Spot realized his hands were stuck together again. Tree frogs stick to everything, even \emp\themselves sometimes.</page1>
        <page2>\Pit=400\\Spd=175\"What do you think is in it, Bonzi?" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\asked Spot, wide-eyed and practically drooling with excitement!\Pit=50\"\Map="Probably \emp\fantastic \emp\jewer\emp\lee and \emp\gold coins and \emp\bananas,"="Probably fantastic jewerlry and gold coins and bananas,"\" \Pit=140\said a \emp\confident Bonzi. By now, the fog was starting to clear, but neither Bonzi or Spot noticed the cruise ship on the horizon! \Pit=400\\Spd=175\"Wow! Do you think we should try to open it?" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Spot. \Pit=50\"Of course! Here, help me," \Pit=140\directed Bonzi. Together they pushed and pulled, but they were unable to get it open! Spot said \Pit=400\\Spd=175\"I think we need some help, Bonzi." \Pit=50\\Spd=150\"\Map="Hummm,"="Hmmm,"\ I think you're right. Let's go get the others," \Pit=140\said Bonzi.</page2>
        <page3>Together, they dug a hole and buried the chest for safe keeping! Then they went to go get their friends, Tiggs, Raffie, and Tuck! Down by the waterhole, they found them all discussing what to get Effie for her birthday! When Bonzi and Spot got there, they were out of breath from running, and so excited about what they had found that they had a hard time telling them! Finally, Bonzi blurted out \Pit=50\"We found a Treasure Chest!" \Pit=400\\Spd=175\"Yes and it's full of fantastic jewerly and gold coins and bananas!" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\added Spot, who was jumping up and down!</page3>
        <page4>\Pit=400\\Spd=150\"Wow! This is delightfully devine," \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Raffie imagining herself adorned with \emp\jewels. \Pit=100\"Way cool!" \Pit=140\said Tiggs imagining all the \emp\great \emp\things he would buy with his new found \emp\wealth. \Pit=50\\Spd=50\ "Are you sure it's a Treasure Chest and not just some old box full of seaweed?" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Tuck, who couldn't understand what the hoopla was all about! \Pit=50\"How about we go find \emp\out?" \Pit=140\said Bonzi.</page4>
        <page5>Off they went, \emp\back down to the \emp\beach. Sure enough, the chest was where they had \emp\left it. Bonzi, Spot, and Tiggs tried to open it again, but had no such \emp\luck. Finally Tuck said, \Pit=50\\Spd=50\"Why don't you try undoing the latch first? Spot, hop over there and push that latch through, then just lift it up." \Pit=140\\Spd=150\Spot did what Tuck said, while Bonzi, Tiggs, and Raffie, looked on! \Pit=100\"Very funny Tuck,  you could have told us that a long time ago," \Pit=140\said Tiggs. Tuck chuckled to himself, \Pit=50\\Spd=50\"But it was too entertaining watching the three of you." \Pit=400\\Spd=150\"\Map="OK"="O.K."\ we all had a good laugh. Open it up!" \Pit=140\"said Raffie, who couldn't stand waiting one minute longer!</page5>
        <page6>\emp\Bonzi \emp\slowly lifted the \emp\lid of the chest, but as \emp\soon as \emp\he saw all the bright colors and objects that \emp\appeared to look like \emp\precious \emp\jewels, he quickly flung the lid open and began throwing out all the magnificent items to his friends around him!</page6>
        <page7>\Pit=50\\Spd=50\"It appears we have found a chest full of party costumes. How perfect for Effie's surprise party tonight," \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Tuck. \Pit=50\\Spd=50\"Personally I would like to wear that top hat and scarf, if it's OK with you Bonzi. I know these items belong to you and Spot, because you found them, but may I borrow them for this evening?" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\asked an ever so polite Tuck. \Pit=50\"You can most certainly have this top hat and \emp\scarf, Tuck. Keep them, they fit you well!" \Pit=140\said Bonzi, as he \emp\tied the \emp\scarf \emp\neatly around his \emp\neck.</page7>
        <page8>\Pit=100\"May I have this cool tuxedo jacket Bonzi? It fits me perfectly!" \Pit=140\asked Tiggs. \Pit=50\"You bet! It looks great on you!" \Pit=140\said Bonzi.</page8>
        <page9>\Pit=400\\Spd=175\"Help!" \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Spot, \Pit=400\\Spd=175\"I seem to be stuck to this red thing!" \Pit=50\\Spd=150\"That's not a red thing, that's a cape and it's fit for a king!" \Pit=140\said Bonzi, \Pit=50\"and since you're stuck to it and you go where I go, I guess I must be the King!" \Pit=140\They all laughed, as Bonzi tied the cape around his neck, which left Spot stucked to his shoulder!</page9>
        <page10>\Pit=50\"Look at this great feather boa, Raffie! This would be terrific on you," \Pit=140\said Bonzi. \emp\Raffie \emp\liked the \emp\feather \emp\boa, but she saw herself in \emp\jewels.</page10>
        <page11>That's when Bonzi pulled out the most amazing item of all! It shimmered in the sunlight, which had broken through the \emp\clouds, and it displayed the most beautiful colors any of them had ever seen! It was a tiara \emp\laced in \emp\diamonds, which they all thought were real! \Pit=50\"Won't this make the most \emp\incredible birthday gift for Effie?" \Pit=140\said Bonzi.</page11>
        <page12>Just as everyone was agreeing with Bonzi, Raffie said, \Pit=400\\Spd=150\"That's mine! I need that! I'm the one who should be wearing diamonds and not Effie," \Pit=140\\Spd=150\ and she grabbed it right out of Bonzi's hands! Shocked, everyone just stared at Raffie! \Pit=50\\Spd=50\"It's not yours Raffie. It belongs to Bonzi and Spot they should decide who they give it to," \Pit=140\\Spd=150\said Tuck.</page12>
        <page13>\Pit=50\"Gee, I wish I had never found this dumb Treasure \emp\Chest," \Pit=140\said Bonzi sadly. The others \emp\agreed. Then all of them, \emp\except Raffie, put their costumes back into the \emp\chest. Then, one by one, they left Raffie standing \emp\there, as they each went off to get \emp\ready for the \emp\party.</page13>
        <page14>"Surprise!" they all yelled as Effie showed up at Bonzi's hut! \emp\Everyone was there but Raffie. \Pit=125\"Where's Raffie?" \Pit=140\asked Effie, \Pit=125\"It's not a party without \emp\her here too." \Pit=50\"I'm not sure Effie, but \emp\we're all here and we've made these \emp\gifts for you," \Pit=140\said Bonzi, trying to hide his disappointment with his \emp\brilliant smile. Bonzi handed Effie the \emp\seashell frame that \emp\Spot and \emp\he had made. \emp\Tuck \emp\gave her \emp\words of \emp\advice and \emp\Tiggs gave her a shawl that he had made from banana \emp\leaves. Then they all sang "Happy Birthday!" to her! Effie made a \emp\wish and blew out the candles on her banana cream \emp\cake, when a familiar voice said...</page14>
        <page15>\Pit=400\"You can't have cake without me. Besides, I have the best gift of all to give you," \Pit=140\said Raffie. \Pit=400\"Today I realized something very important Effie. The most important treasure we have in our lives is our friends. No amount of gifts can make you feel as happy as the love you recieve from them. So, happy birthday Effie! You are loved by us all, especially me." \Pit=140\There wasn't a dry eye in the house as Raffie placed the tiara on Effie's head! \Pit=125\\Spd=125\"Thank you Everyone! My birthday wish has come true! I just wanted you all to be here with \emp\me," \Pit=140\\Spd=150\Effie said.</page15>
        <page16>"Hurray!" they all yelled and clapped except for Spot whose hands always got stuck \Map="together!.... The end!"="together! THE END!"\"\</page16>
